{"type": "article", "id": 63154, "title": "Gucci  新广告片还原古希腊聚会，81 岁女性登上 Vogue 封面 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-04-22T05:05:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 137, "name": "女性"}, {"id": 4489, "name": "代言"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190422124420nDK3UwZamtRk80lp.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"Fykk\"><b><a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/sergiorossi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">古力娜扎成为 Sergio Rossi 大中华区首位代言人</a>，</b>上周的代言人预热海报设计得不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124531MgIZkCDRz2BvLSq9.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124531NdALb2hefIxUwBzj.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124532Ud85MrFCx7cje06K.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124532lfxPkN7DZA1T95v2.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.984259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"76Mf\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1862743514/4363061575877410\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">马思纯成为百丽首位品牌代言人</a>。</b>百丽之前还和星座博主同道大叔合作，推出 12 星座限量鞋款。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124601F1OZPL5aY64IDNhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"4ZCs\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4362725847313918?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">匡威签下篮球运动员阿不都沙拉木为品牌代言人</a>，</b> 还将于 5 月首先在美国发售 “All Star Pro BB” 新款篮球鞋，该产品将于 6 月在中国市场上市。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124613qZwcs34SJhHALEfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"4GD9\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1687422352/4362049905648248\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">肯德基口袋炸鸡店在品牌代言人鹿晗 4 月 17 日生日之际，开启“一‘鹿’相伴生日趴”。</a> </b>用户可以参与开店、加糖、买生日餐为生日趴点亮星光。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124701CL0NF3TdtPz2qMy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124702ab647Dzylm20Xr1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.718667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"TTfX\"><b>Nike 上海举办“狂想集结站”创意工坊，</b>活动现场耐克设计师、客座大师和创意达人们分享了创意想法和技艺，之后引导参与课程的学员完成命题创作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124733pUNTxitamhXKqnGY.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.478750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904221247337vOQaINGoXn60myl.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904221247333FrHf8g71CoMRNqv.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124734PyV8tRAq7hCQ1fm3.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.884375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124734ZskJghayC9pbYFMX.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124734byre9uQKUsiIYDkf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124735MptEdvNhnRrTfa40.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124735XE5dUOmLt8ITcMQl.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124735qsBQbR9oTrFcW3JH.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124736W5tolpDzYZOK0mSf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124737C4MNqrhOHR6xYAkz.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"FRSu\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1934738161/4362759589669718\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gucci 发布 2019 年秋季广告片。</b></a>拍摄地选在了意大利西溪里塞利农特的古代神庙，身着 Gucci 最新一季服饰的模特们在旧废墟边聚会，依然充满复古气息。品牌解释场景源自古希腊与伊特鲁里亚时代的聚会风俗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0862i6zfdo\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"hwuY\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/british-vogue-partnered-with-loreal-and-mccann-to-publish-an-80-page-non-issue-on-aging/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>欧莱雅和英版 Vogue 合作推出 “non-issue”（非问题）特别版五月刊，</b></a>杂志中涵盖了一系列 50 岁以上女性的故事，借此打破对女性的年龄成见。81 岁的奥斯卡影后 Jane Fonda 登上封面，欧莱雅还在本月初签下 51 岁的 Celine Dion ，后者成为品牌最新全球代言人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124820LefXYVACDGvUO0I4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124820O0sxJI7uECqH3pNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.297273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124820QTEweg0VnWjM87rx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422124821yN9zmds62B8LTaAC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"jBRg\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/sjxGWcj5nKE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>折扣店 TK Maxx 拍了支百老汇歌舞剧风格的广告片 <em>The Right Way</em>。</b></a>华丽搞笑的风格希望消费者到店购买便宜商品，即使没时间，还有线上网站。创意代理商是 W+K。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0863stej2z\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3><b>其他，也很重要</b></h3><p line=\"ETRg\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/media/warnermedia-pulls-out-openap/2165706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>华纳正在退出受众定位平台 OpenAP。</b></a>后者由 Turner（现在为华纳传媒）、福克斯和威亚康姆于 2017 年成立，希望能将推荐广告销售标准化。</p><p line=\"ETRg\">这一举动应该还是和 AT&amp;T 收购华纳后重组业务有关。它去年成立广告公司 Xander，后者负责所有广告和分析业务，意味着可能会和 OpenAP 构成直接竞争关系。</p><p line=\"ETRg\" class=\"\">题图来自：TK Maxx</p>"}